interfaces.ITestCase

  • Packages that use ITestCase 
    Package Description
    data
    This package contains all classes for Excel Runner classes which read data from Excel Workbooks and allow the keywordProvider to run data-driven tests
    framework
    This package contains all base KeywordProvider classes
    interfaces
    public interfaces for defining the model of how the keywordProvider works with keywords, logging, and Excel workbooks.
